headline: Does the Recent 8% Drop in Freeport-McMoRan Signal a New Opportunity in 2025?
summary: If you have been wondering what to do with your Freeport-McMoRan shares, or considering jumping in for the first time, you are not alone. This miner has drawn plenty of curious eyes lately, as its stock price has ridden a mix of market moods, sector shifts, and big-picture headlines.
